# Load preprocessed data
d <- fread("../../data/processed/pretest.csv")
corrplot.mixed <- function(data) {
  colnames(data) <- gsub("_", "\n", colnames(data))
  corrplot::corrplot.mixed(cor(data), order="hclust", tl.col="black")
}
